{"tid":2017173,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發] 全部小朋友同我立即認真讀書, 考好DSE","createTime":"2020-05-15T02:54:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T03:23:57.000Z","uid":192420,"like":17,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1702c5ffbca661b9b13d8d91cd58a4b0a976b281","tid":2017173,"uid":192420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:54:34.000Z","msg":"我知道呢1,2年嘅事，令好多年輕人對未來冇希望，好想放棄，甚至有身心創傷，或者已離開咗我哋，無法再做到想做嘅事。但正正因為咁，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">餘下嘅我們更加需要努力行好革命呢條路。</span></strong></span>小朋友我想你地認真讀書，借你3分鐘睇睇點解。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/images/2711048c043a8d1d7b20b17d57ba0e5b/tenor.gif?itemid=14784999\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.tenor.com%2Fimages%2F2711048c043a8d1d7b20b17d57ba0e5b%2Ftenor.gif%3Fitemid%3D14784999&h=33d6e150&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個係一場時代革命，要建立新世界，需要時日，需要實力。</span></span></strong>許多智者如攬炒巴等已經分析過，我哋要鏟除獨裁政權之餘，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">最重要係重新建立我哋嘅民主社會，一個可持續發展嘅國家－－香港，需要匯集文、武、財三大範疇嘅精英同實力</span></span></strong>：<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">議會（有識之士、立法者）；軍力（軍隊及外地軍火）；財團（就業及發展機會）；外交（軍事經濟聯盟）。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新香港需要勇武，亦需要賢明嘅智者同財主各司其職。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好因為覺得做唔到勇武就冇用，冇打傷幾隻狗就叫冇參與革命，千析唔好咁諗。<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">相反，你要認清楚自己擁有咩能力，未來可以發展成為一個怎樣有用嘅人，怎樣可以幫到呢場革命，幫到香港建國。</span></span></strong>例如，你口才好，應該要學好正體中文同廣東話，學多幾種外語，幫助向海外宣傳革命及新香港，吸納海外資金，資源同人才，為未來民主政權鋪路。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇到高官、紅底法官嘅荒謬言論，你好嬲好嬲，更加要認清一個事實－－<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">上到位唔係因為正直、公義、同情心，而係因為佢識玩，有技巧，有資源。</span></span></strong>就算做律師咁又點？係因為佢有辦法考到，而唔係因為佢好人。我哋已經好清楚，社會已經分崩離析，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我哋要思想、行動同能力上武裝自己。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以，作為學生嘅你，唔好擔心大人嗰part，我哋會一齊努力。請你趁學習期間盡力吸收知識，擴闊眼界。</span></span></strong>功利咁講。DSE就係其中一個TASK。<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">盡力考好佢，令呢個遊戲得到嘅「入場劵」同「道具」愈來愈多。</span></strong> 成為一個有獨立思考嘅人，亦非常重要。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真正攬炒嘅意思，唔係鬥流血冚家產，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要「先破後立」</span></strong></span>。即係藍絲仆街，而我哋係最終笑住贏嗰個。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n應承我，永遠懷住革命之火，把握每一日，每次機會，我哋一齊喺不同嘅崗位盡力。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">星星之火，可以燎原</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gifer.com/6hrS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gifer.com%2F6hrS.gif&h=250a2169&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gifer.com/7DtF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gifer.com%2F7DtF.gif&h=f6a45b32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gifer.com/4qum.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gifer.com%2F4qum.gif&h=52fb1e0c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b98f4c1f5a640b94b494eafcf0cc0872d66c593","tid":2017173,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:55:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"73bc5777cabb93bfb2960bd20c146900f2fa10f3","tid":2017173,"uid":263618,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:56:12.000Z","msg":"新香港需要勇武<br />\n<br />\nthis 反對<br />\n未見過有人搞革命係用umbrella but 冇武器嘅<br />\n你咁樣即係推啲年青人去死"},{"pid":"07e13cecd2ef10610d13cbd5bbb0ae377da9aec7","tid":2017173,"uid":192420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73bc5777cabb93bfb2960bd20c146900f2fa10f3","tid":2017173,"uid":263618,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:56:12.000Z","msg":"新香港需要勇武<br />\n<br />\nthis 反對<br />\n未見過有人搞革命係用umbrella but 冇武器嘅<br />\n你咁樣即係推啲年青人去死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:57:39.000Z","msg":"上面提咗：香港，需要匯集文、武、財三大範疇嘅精英同實力：議會（有識之士、立法者）；<span style=\"color: red;\">軍力（軍隊及外地軍火）</span>；財團（就業及發展機會）；外交（軍事經濟聯盟）。"},{"pid":"00bbf10cf393076152a218d7a25473f0c2081a51","tid":2017173,"uid":30084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:59:05.000Z","msg":"地下獨立黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e867fdcd18d3847ba4227122c062668919bab0","tid":2017173,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T03:08:31.000Z","msg":"仲DSE<br />\n睇怕下年DSE份卷要林鄭批准<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0229f369ee9c10846b6f598c3921f91c1dff510c","tid":2017173,"uid":26953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T03:09:51.000Z","msg":"你依家講D小朋友都溫唔切書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下年早D講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4742332c1589be2969d6c10efc427ff82a01a4e","tid":2017173,"uid":192420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0229f369ee9c10846b6f598c3921f91c1dff510c","tid":2017173,"uid":26953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T03:09:51.000Z","msg":"你依家講D小朋友都溫唔切書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下年早D講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T03:19:04.000Z","msg":"咁岩而家最後衝刺嘛，讀好啲書，DSE只係其中一個task，盡做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16dd4045f96d228893f96891723da0080f13576c","tid":2017173,"uid":192420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"26e867fdcd18d3847ba4227122c062668919bab0","tid":2017173,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T03:08:31.000Z","msg":"仲DSE<br />\n睇怕下年DSE份卷要林鄭批准<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T03:21:23.000Z","msg":"個試緊係有問題，<br />\n但始終呢個試對學生好重要。<br />\n唔可以因為咁就叫佢哋放棄"},{"pid":"6027dff8d9dfb6d65b0ee3800e4eea688dc732ba","tid":2017173,"uid":192420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T03:23:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">負皮嘅人答我，點解你唔贊成叫學生努力讀書？<br />\n除非你本身係戇鳩嘅毅進狗，驚人叻過你。</span>"},{"pid":"53f8cf55b134693a4c7dd55a7c6c8bc1d75a4fce","tid":2017173,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T03:23:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推 奪回香港"},{"pid":"7739ce22f18251dcef38a618b2e63ffc5e8cfcfe","tid":2017173,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6027dff8d9dfb6d65b0ee3800e4eea688dc732ba","tid":2017173,"uid":192420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T03:23:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">負皮嘅人答我，點解你唔贊成叫學生努力讀書？<br />\n除非你本身係戇鳩嘅毅進狗，驚人叻過你。</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T03:23:57.000Z","msg":"讀書不如拎學費去利疊利"}]}